MBOMBELA &#8211; A business situated in Stinkhout Crescent was robbed this morning when suspects entered the premises and held the staff up at gunpoint and tied them up.According to Hi-Tech CSG Holdings Lowveld response manager Callum Mac Pherson, they were alerted when some of the staff managed to free themselves and alert a neighboring business. He said the suspects stole an undisclosed amount of cash and fled the scene in a white Toyota Avanza.This is a developing story and Lowvelder will update as soon as more information becomes available.